org.labrad.qubits.proxies
Class DeconvolutionProxy

java.lang.Object
  org.labrad.qubits.proxies.DeconvolutionProxy

public class DeconvolutionProxy
extends Object

This class gives us a way to ask for data to be deconvolved before we pass it to the DACs to be executed. Currently, this works by sending requests to the DAC Calibration server, which does the actual work.
